<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q1_v11" title="Operaciones_con_enteros_secuencia" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>
        Se parte del número <m:math><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:math>. Primero se resta 7, luego el resultado se multiplica por −3 y, finalmente, se suma 5. ¿Cuál es el resultado final de esta secuencia de operaciones?
      </qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">−28<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al seguir la secuencia indicada: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−11</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>−3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>33</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y finalmente <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>33</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el resultado final no es <m:math><m:mn>−28</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">−4<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si se realizan todas las operaciones del enunciado, se obtiene: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, después <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−11</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>−3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>33</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>33</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso, el resultado final no es <m:math><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">38<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La secuencia es: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−11</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>−3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>33</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y finalmente <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>33</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el resultado final es <m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">10<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El cálculo completo es: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, después <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−11</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>−3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>33</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y al sumar 5 se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>33</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces, el resultado final no es <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Partir del número inicial</strong></p>
            <p>El número inicial es <m:math><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Restar 7</strong></p>
            <p>Se calcula:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Después de la primera operación, el resultado es <m:math><m:mn>−11</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Multiplicar el resultado por −3</strong></p>
            <p>Ahora se calcula:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−11</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>−3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>33</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Como el producto de dos números negativos es positivo, se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>33</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Sumar 5</strong></p>
            <p>Finalmente:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>33</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El resultado final de la secuencia de operaciones es <m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>C</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>